<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Wewe Umechoka Sana? TZR53</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Wewe umechoka sana?
 Wataka raha?
 Kwake Yesu utapata furaha.

[V2]
 Alama anazo yeye?
 Sasa! makovu ya mikono, na miguu,
 Na mbavu.

[V3]
 Nacho kimivukwa taji
 Kichwa cha huba?
 Alivikwa taji kweli miiba.

[V4]
 Huku nikimfuata nipate nini?
 Maonjo nje na ndani amani.

[V5]
 Kwamba namwandama Bwana,
 Mwisho ni nini?
 Ni furaha na salama
 Mbinguni.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>53</hymn_number>
</song>